{"tid":1411320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂我地都要每日開記招呀 攞翻個話語權呀","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:43:28.000Z","uid":126612,"like":141,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"e91cc21a48dde3f33c5aa7178778b83903e1eab0","tid":1411320,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:25:28.000Z","msg":"每日譴責政府唔回應<br />\n圖文片並茂<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每日黑警做左啲乜犯法野</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每日同政府講<br />\n係佢地搞亂香港<br />\n立即回應訴求<br />\n先可以停止亂象<br />\n<br />\n唔可以淨係得佢地日日洗腦<br />\n我地都要每日提醒大家政府黑警做左乜仆街野<br />\n<br />\nStyle最好完全跟足對家<br />\n減低入屋成本"},{"pid":"06e15a9bddd8edf7e0250a3c1a9b7e9782511d91","tid":1411320,"uid":34457,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"你開有鬼用 冇電視台會播<br />\n要推泛民出黎開"},{"pid":"5a948bef3d875947e0e88939aa72e0ecfe932d8a","tid":1411320,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"八五罷工 七區集會<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5c019d90cca8a4cdcd6fced84112ed7d07f56fc6","tid":1411320,"uid":126612,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06e15a9bddd8edf7e0250a3c1a9b7e9782511d91","tid":1411320,"uid":34457,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"你開有鬼用 冇電視台會播<br />\n要推泛民出黎開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"咪就係要有話語權既人開囉"},{"pid":"0eb87d8a10ccc4818516aa3a2a159a9cdbae29a4","tid":1411320,"uid":126612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"八五罷工 七區集會<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"92d5ed87794b8cc209f838a499ae30caed6b8cf3","tid":1411320,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"叫政黨做"},{"pid":"d59dc4c304dbc5f716264eaa1940d5219a5944d8","tid":1411320,"uid":14026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"借泛民既力<br />\n搵市民講<